==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
*From κῦρος kuros (supremacy); supreme in authority, that is, (as noun) controller; by implication Mr. (as a respectful title): 

===Pronunciation===
*κύριος  kurios koo'-ree-os

===Noun===
# [[God]], [[Lord]], [[master]], [[Sir]].

